\v 8 Kodwa ngizatshiya insali\x + 12.16. 14.22.\x* ukuze libe l\add abanye\add* abazaphepha inkemba phakathi kwezizwe\x + 6.9. 7.16. Jer. 44.28.\x* lapho lizahlakazekela emazweni\x + 5.10.\x*.
\v 9 Labaphunyukileyo benu\x + 6.9. 7.16. Jer. 44.28.\x* bazangikhumbula phakathi kwezizwe lapho abathunjelwe khona\x + 12.16. 14.22.\x*\x + 20.43. 36.31. Levi 26.39. Hos. 5.15.\x*; ngoba ngidabukile ngenxa yenhliziyo yabo ephingayo, esukileyo kimi\x + Jer. 23.9. Hlab. 78.40. Isa. 7.13. 43.24. 63.10.\x*, langamehlo abo\x + 20.7,24. Nani 15.39. Jobe 31.7.\x* aphingayo elandela izithombe zabo\x + 23.30. Eks. 34.15.\x*. Njalo bazazenyanya ngobubi ababenzileyo kuwo wonke amanyala abo\x + 20.43. 36.31. Levi 26.39. Hos. 5.15.\x*\x + 16.47. Jobe 10.1. Hlab. 95.10. 119.158. 139.21. Jobe 42.6.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo bazakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 6.13. 7.4,9. 11.10,12. 12.20. 13.9,14,21,23. 14.8. 15.7. 16.62. 20.38,42,44. 22.16. 23.49. 24.24. 25.5,7. 35.4,9,12. 36.11. 37.6,13. 6.10,14. 4.27. 12.15,16. 20.26. 24.27. 25.11,17. 26.6. 28.22,23,24,26. 29.6,9,16,21. 30.8,19,25,26. 32.15. 33.29. 34.27. 35.15. 36.23,38. 38.23. 39.6,7,22,28. Jow. 2.27. 3.17. Hlab. 9.16. Eks. 7.5.\x*\nd*; kangikhulumanga\x + 5.13.\x* ngeze ukuthi ngizakwenza lokho okubi kubo\x + 14.23.\x*.
