\v 11 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Tshaya ngesandla sakho\x + 21.14.\x*, utshaye phansi ngonyawo lwakho\x + 25.6.\x*, uthi: Maye ngenxa yawo wonke amanyala amabi endlu yakoIsrayeli! Ngoba bazakuwa ngenkemba, ngendlala, langomatshayabhuqe wesifo\x + 7.15. 5.12. Jer. 42.17,22.\x*.
\v 12 Okhatshana uzakufa ngomatshayabhuqe wesifo, loseduze uzakuwa ngenkemba, loseleyo wavinjezelwa uzakufa yindlala\x + 7.15. 5.12. Jer. 42.17,22.\x*. Ngokunjalo ngizaphelelisa ukufutheka kwami phezu kwabo\x + 5.13.\x*.
