\v 14 Ngokunjalo ngizakwelulela isandla sami phezu kwabo\x + 25.7,13,16. 35.3. Isa. 5.25.\x*, ngenze ilizwe libe lunxiwa, yebo, libe lunxiwa kulenkangala\x + 33.28.\x* ngaseDibila\x + Nani 33.46. Jer. 48.22.\x*, kuzo zonke izindawo zabo zokuhlala\x + 6.6.\x*. Khona bezakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 6.13. 7.4,9. 11.10,12. 12.20. 13.9,14,21,23. 14.8. 15.7. 16.62. 20.38,42,44. 22.16. 23.49. 24.24. 25.5,7. 35.4,9,12. 36.11. 37.6,13. 6.10,14. 4.27. 12.15,16. 20.26. 24.27. 25.11,17. 26.6. 28.22,23,24,26. 29.6,9,16,21. 30.8,19,25,26. 32.15. 33.29. 34.27. 35.15. 36.23,38. 38.23. 39.6,7,22,28. Jow. 2.27. 3.17. Hlab. 9.16. Eks. 7.5.\x*\nd*.
